OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright but rather cloudy with
OL,6,Fisolated outbreaks of light rain for
OL,7,FArgyll, especially in the afternoon.
OL,8,FSome hazy sunnier spells are possible,
OL,9,Fmainly for the Glasgow area. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry and bright this
OL,13,Fevening, but with the chance of a few
OL,14,Flight spots of rain, especially across
OL,15,FArgyll. Further showers may develop
OL,16,Ftowards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
