OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy morning with a
OL,6,Ffew light showers. Brighter and drier
OL,7,Fconditions develop in the afternoon
OL,8,Ffor Argyll, though a few showers may
OL,9,Fstill affect the Glasgow area.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,12,Fand settled conditions prevail through
OL,13,Fthis period with light winds. Patchy
OL,14,Fcloud develops on Tuesday, before
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine is expected on
OL,16,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
